Common.Highlight.Common.Text: 9,855 SF Office Building with Retail Frontage

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: 600 Main is located within a qualified opportunity zone, providing tax advantages to investors. The property is located on a prominent corner, just 1 mile from downtown Nashville and offers easy access to surrounding neighborhoods and major interstates. 600 Main offers easy access to a variety of popular East Nashville restaurants, bars, and music/arts venues.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: CBRE is pleased to announce for sale, 600 Main Street, a 9,855 square foot Office/Retail Building in East Nashville. Located on a main thoroughfare, the site is in close proximity and offers easy access to Downtown Nashville, area amenities, and Nashville’s hottest neighborhoods. The property has a WalkScore of 81, which is considered “very walkable” to surrounding amenities.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: 9,855 SF East Nashville Building For Sale

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: The property is located on a prominent corner, just 2 miles from downtown Nashville and offers easy access to surrounding neighborhoods and major interstates.

directly south of downtown, the site is in close proximity and offers easy access to area amenities, Class A developments, and Nashville’s hottest neighborhoods.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text:
Germantown is a historic neighborhood that continues to see growth, transformation, and revitalization, creating an attractive live, work, play community where one can enjoy all the benefits of its award-winning dining
scene, and walkability. An urban community with a charming vibe, Germantown is a vibrant place that easily attracts new businesses and residents alike.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: CBRE is pleased to offer for sale or lease, 600 4th Ave N, a 7,900 SF office building situated where Nashville’s CBD and Germantown neighborhood meet. The property is highly walkable to a variety of nearby amenities and offers a unique branding and signage opportunity.
